“Prophets, pastors, preachers alike. Everybody telling me everything, pushing this way and that. It’s like something was deliberately confusing me.” “As young as I was, I felt old, fragile, the music industry is a horrible place. I was attacked constantly online and the labels, it was like they didn’t take me seriously.” Gigi explained how emotional she was after she was shown her fourth generation ancestors. “[I] Get there and there was this warmth. The warmth I used to feel surrounding me when I used to dream of my khokho and gogo. She took me four generations back before I was born! I almost ran out screaming. To top it all off, my family confirmed everything."